title: Welcome!
text: This website is a repository of all the technical notes on my professional life.

title: About
text:
Soil Scientist, Data Analyst and an active learner of new things.
Currently I am a Faculty of the Department of Plant and Soil Science, College of Agriculture and Agri-industries (CAA), Caraga State University (CSU) since 2015.
